title: Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Rogue Spear Collection
description:
The second installment to the infamous Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six franchise, Rogue Spear improves upon the famous tactical shooter enhancing both graphics and gameplay.

This pack includes:
- Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Rogue Spear
- Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Rogue Spear -- Urban Operations
- Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Covert Ops Essentials
- Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Rogue Spear-- Black Thorn.

To install, mount images and then install (use compatibility mode for Vista/Seven users), preferrably in the order of release.

Optional: download no CD fixes from the web and crack.

Language: English (plus more?)
